description:
7 in 1 Portable Beauty Make up Cosmetic Trolley Case Black

This beauty is a 4-level aluminium trolley case. It is big in size, but transporting will not be a burden as it is equipped with a pull-out wheeler travel handle maKing transporting a breeze. The top compartment is detachable and is convenient to carry for short trips. Whether it is a job where you'll need all or few tools, you can easily remove or add on the number of middle section with the side locks.

With plenty of storage space, it will make organising much easier. You can even customise the way you want everything to be placed with the adjustable dividers. No matter the size or amount of tools required for the job, this beauty will provide all the space you need.

Whether a professional beautician or amateur nail tech, this stunning, stylish 7 In 1 Make Up Cosmetic Beauty Case will have everything right beside you as you need it!

Features

    Durable aluminium frame and hinges
    4 layers in 1 makeup trolley
    Separable & portable beauty case
    Equipped with a pull-out wheeler travel handle
    Elegant black velvet interior lining
    4 sliding trays and durable handle on the top case
    4 removable & adjustable dividers
    8 locks with 2 keys
    4 non-slippery feet on the top and middle section cases
    Exterior material: Aluminium frame
    Interior material: Velvet lining
    Dimension: 35x25x75cm
    Weight: 7.5kg
    Colour: Black

Package Contents

    1 x 7 In 1 Make Up Beauty Case

This product comes with 1 year warranty
name: Embellir 1EACH
